title: Devendra Fadnavis’ Maha push: Maharashtra to become $1 trillion economy by 2025? The road ahead
dc:creator: FE Online
content: Maha Push: Stating his strategy for growth in the state of Maharashtra, Chief Minister Devendra Fadnavis said that the state aspires to become a $1 trillion economy by 2025.
